  "title": "Admin Accounts Clerk",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description:</h3><ul><li><p>Update daily sales and expense transactions into the accounting system</p></li><li><p>Reconcile marketplace payments (e.g. platform sales vs bank receipts)</p></li><li><p>Assist with invoice issuance and filing</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper records and documentation</p></li><li><p>Support basic accounts receivable and payable matters</p></li><li><p>Perform other administrative and accounts-related duties as assigned</p></li></ul><h3>Job Requirements:</h3><ul><li><p>Basic knowledge of accounting or bookkeeping</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with data entry and reconciliation work</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Microsoft Excel</p></li><li><p>Careful, organised, and detail-oriented</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and follow instructions</p></li><li><p>Experience in accounting or admin roles is an advantage (training provided)</p></li></ul><h3>Benefits:</h3><ul><li><p>4-day work week (Friday to Sunday off)</p></li><li><p>Short working hours (10:00am – 5:00pm)</p></li><li><p>Stable and friendly working environment</p></li><li><p>14 days annual leave</p></li></ul>",
